[gd_scene load_steps=6 format=3 uid="uid://calimabaseart1"]

; Base artifact — ordinary, common restorables. Open this scene to change the model and
; to add/move/remove ArtifactConditionDecal children (each one is a condition; its
; texture file name decides the type + which tool cleans it). "Randomized Decal Count" on
; the root picks how many of the placed conditions appear on any one run (re-rolled each
; loop / new save). Set it to 0 to always show them all.

